code:
---
config:
  theme: redux
---
flowchart TD
    A1[FinTech_AuthVault] --> A[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    A --> B[FinTech_LedgerService]
    B -- Memory read successful --> C[FinTech_LedgerService]
    B -- Memory access error --> D[FinTech_LedgerService]
    D --> E[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    E --> F[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    C --> G{FinTech_FraudDetection}
    G -- Yes --> H[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    G -- No --> I[FinTech_LedgerService]
    I --> J[FinTech_LedgerService]
    J --> K[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    K --> A
    H --> L{FinTech_AuthVault}
    L -- Immediate, Implied, Accumulator --> M[FinTech_LedgerService]
    L -- Zero Page, Indexed, Absolute --> N[FinTech_AuthVault]
    L -- Indirect, Relative --> O[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    M --> P[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    N --> Q[FinTech_AuthVault]
    O --> R[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    P --> S[FinTech_AuthVault]
    Q --> S
    R --> S
    S --> T{FinTech_LedgerService}
    T -- "Arithmetic/Logical - e.g., ADC, AND" --> U[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    T -- "Load/Store - e.g., LDA, STA" --> V[FinTech_LedgerService]
    T -- "Branch - e.g., BEQ, JMP" --> W[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    T -- "Stack - e.g., PHA, RTS" --> X[FinTech_AuthVault]
    T -- "System - e.g., BRK, RTI" --> Y[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    U --> Z[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    V --> Z
    W --> AA[FinTech_LedgerService]
    X --> Z
    Y --> AB[FinTech_AuthVault]
    AA -- Met --> AC[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    AA --  Not mett --> AD[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    AC --> Z
    AD --> Z
    AB -- Interrupt triggered --> AE[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    AB -- Return from interrupt --> AF[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    AE --> AG[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    AF --> Z
    Z --> AH[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    AG --> AH
    AH --> AI{FinTech_LedgerService}
    AI -- "NMI pending - e.g., PPU VBlank" --> AJ[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    AI -- "IRQ pending - e.g., mapper, APU" --> AK[FinTech_FraudDetection]
    AI -- No interrupts --> AL[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    AJ --> AM[FinTech_LedgerService]
    AK --> AN[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    AL --> AO[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    AM --> AO
    AN --> AO
    AO --> AP{FinTech_PaymentGateway}
    AP -- Yes --> AQ[FinTech_LedgerService]
    AQ --> AR[FinTech_AuthVault]
    AR --> AS[FinTech_PaymentGateway]
    AS --> AT[FinTech_TransactionQueue]
    AT --> AU[FinTech_AuthVault]
    AP -- No --> AU
    AU --> A
    style AI stroke:#000000
repo_description: A Nintendo Entertainment System Emulator written in Swift
